plt.figure(figsize = (20, 10))

for i in range(len(obj_list) - 9):
    obj_count = pd.DataFrame()
    obj_count['고객 수'] = df[obj_list[i]].value_counts()
    
    if obj_list[i] == '서비스이용일그룹':
        obj_count['index'] = [5,4,3,2,1]
        obj_count.sort_values(by = 'index', inplace = True)
    elif obj_list[i] == '약정종료':
        obj_count['index'] = [10, 1, 6, 3, 5, 4, 2, 9, 8, 7]
        obj_count.sort_values(by = 'index', inplace = True)
    elif obj_list[i] == '상품명그룹':
        obj_count['index'] = [3, 4, 1, 2, 5, 6]
        obj_count.sort_values(by = 'index', inplace = True)
    
    plt.subplot(2, 5, i+1)
    sns.barplot(x = obj_count.index, y = '고객 수', data = obj_count, palette='Blues_r', order = obj_count.index)
    plt.title(obj_list[i])
    plt.xticks(rotation = 90)
    plt.tight_layout()

#렌탈제휴 10건 --> 기타
df['가입경로명'] = np.where(df['가입경로명'] == '렌탈제휴', '기타', df['가입경로명'])

#[총이용일수] 3년 단위로 구간화
bins = [0,1095, 2190, 3285, 4380, 5475,10000000000]
labels = ['3년 미만', '3년이상 6년미만', '6년이상 9년미만', '9년이상 12년미만', '12년이상 15년미만','15년이상']
df['총이용일수'] = pd.cut(df['총이용일수'], bins, right=False, labels=labels)

#[TV가입],[총인터넷가입] 재범주화
df['TV가입'] = np.where(df['TV가입'] == 1, '1건', np.where(df['TV가입'] == 2, '2건', '3건 이상'))
df['총인터넷가입'] = np.where(df['총인터넷가입'] == 0, '0건', np.where(df['총인터넷가입'] == 1, '1건', '2건 이상'))

#[1개월평균채널시청시간] 범주화
bins = [0,0.001, 2.767, 5.33, 8.66, 10000000000]
labels = ['0', '1Q', '2Q', '3Q', '4Q']
df['1개월평균채널시청시간'] = pd.cut(df['1개월평균채널시청시간'], bins, right=False, labels=labels)

#키즈콘텐츠PV
df['키즈컨텐츠PV'] = np.where(df['키즈컨텐츠PV'] == 0, '0건', '1건 이상')

#키즈콘텐츠VOD이용여부
df['키즈컨텐츠VOD이용여부'] = np.where(df['키즈컨텐츠VOD이용여부'] == 0, '0건', '1건 이상')

import matplotlib.ticker as tkr
def yfunc(y, pos):
    s = '{:0,d}'.format(int(y))
    return s

for i in range(len(col_list)):
    plt.figure(figsize = (10, 5))
    fig, axe1 = plt.subplots()

    df2 = pd.DataFrame()
    df2['해지율(%)'] = (df[df['해지여부'] == 'y'][col_list[i]].value_counts() / df[col_list[i]].value_counts()) * 100
    df2['고객 수(명)'] = df[col_list[i]].value_counts()
    if col_list[i] == '서비스이용일그룹':
        df2['index'] = [3,4,5,2,1]
        df2.sort_values(by = 'index', inplace = True)
    elif col_list[i] == '약정종료':
        df2['index'] = [5, 1, 4, 3, 2, 6, 10, 7, 8, 9]
        df2.sort_values(by = 'index', inplace = True)
    elif col_list[i] == '총이용일수':
        df2['index'] = [3, 2, 1, 4, 5, 6]
        df2.sort_values(by = 'index', inplace = True)
    elif col_list[i] == '상품명그룹':
        df2['index'] = [6,3,5,2,4,1]
        df2.sort_values(by = 'index', inplace = True)

    axe2 = axe1.twinx()

    c1 = sns.barplot(ax = axe1, data = df2, x = df2.index, y = '고객 수(명)', palette='Blues_r', hue_order = df2.index)
    c2 = sns.lineplot(x = df2.index, y = '해지율(%)', data = df2, color = 'black', marker="o", hue_order = df2.index)
    # c2 = sns.scatterplot(x = df2.index, y = '해지비율', data = df2, s = 50, color = 'black', hue_order = df2['index'])

    c1.set_xticklabels(c1.get_xticklabels(), rotation=90)

    c1.set_ylabel('고객 수(명)')
    c2.set_ylabel('해지율(%)')
#     c1.set_xlabel(col_list[i])
    c1.set_title(col_list[i])

    # c1.legend(['고객 수'])
    c2.legend(['해지율(%)'])
    plt.show()

#rows, cols는 subplot 개수에 맞게 수정
rows = 10
cols = 2

fig, axes = plt.subplots(nrows = rows, ncols = cols, figsize = (20, 50))

#col_list = 사용할 변수명 list
#df 그래프에 맞게 수정

for i in range(rows):
    for j in range(cols):
    
        df2 = pd.DataFrame()
        df2['해지율(%)'] = (df[df['해지여부'] == 'y'][col_list[i*cols + j]].value_counts() / df[col_list[i*cols + j]].value_counts()) * 100
        df2['고객 수(명)'] = df[col_list[i*cols + j]].value_counts()
        if col_list[i*cols + j] == '서비스이용일그룹':
            df2['index'] = [3,4,5,2,1]
            df2.sort_values(by = 'index', inplace = True)
        elif col_list[i*cols + j] == '약정종료':
            df2['index'] = [5, 1, 4, 3, 2, 6, 10, 7, 8, 9]
            df2.sort_values(by = 'index', inplace = True)
        elif col_list[i*cols + j] == '총이용일수':
            df2['index'] = [3, 2, 1, 4, 5, 6]
            df2.sort_values(by = 'index', inplace = True)
        elif col_list[i*cols + j] == '상품명그룹':
            df2['index'] = [6,3,5,2,4,1]
            df2.sort_values(by = 'index', inplace = True)

        axes2 = axes[i, j].twinx()
        c1 = sns.barplot(ax = axes[i, j], data = df2, x = df2.index, y = '고객 수(명)', palette='Blues_r', hue_order = df2.index)
        c2 = sns.lineplot(x = df2.index, y = '해지율(%)', data = df2, color = 'black', marker="o", hue_order = df2.index)
        
        y_format = tkr.FuncFormatter(yfunc)
        axes[i, j].yaxis.set_major_formatter(y_format)
        
        c1.set_xticklabels(c1.get_xticklabels(), rotation=30)
        c1.set_xlabel(col_list[i*cols + j])
        c2.legend(['해지율(%)'])

        plt.tight_layout()
